node.title: Iraq's PM survives assassination bid by 'booby-trapped' drone
node.alt: Iraq's Prime Minister Mustafa al-Kadhimi inside the White House wearing a white face mask
node.description: Iraq's Prime Minister survivesÂ an assassination attempt as an armed drone targets his residence.
node.content: ["Iraq's Prime Minister Mustafa al-Kadhimi has survived an assassination attempt carried out by an\u00a0armed drone that targeted his residence early on Sunday.", "Two Iraqi officials told the Associated Press that seven security guards were injured in the attack, which occurred in Baghdad's heavily fortified Green Zone area.", "They spoke on condition of anonymity because they were not authorised to give official statements.", "A statement released by state-run media said the failed assassination attempt was with \"a booby-trapped drone that tried to target his residence in the Green Zone\".", "It added that he was not harmed and was in good health.", "Local residents heard the sound of an explosion followed by gunfire.", "The Green Zone houses foreign embassies and government offices.", "\"The security forces are taking the necessary measures in connection with this failed attempt,\" the statement\u00a0said.", "Pro-Iran Shiite militia\u00a0supporters have been camped outside the Green Zone for nearly a month after they rejected the results of Iraq's parliamentary elections in which they were the biggest losers.", "More to come."]
